rComments: She posts TB problems similar to lectures and midterms/final. Very nice and great a answering questions.

Her midterms and exams are exactly like the lectures, and she spends time to make sure everyone understands what is happening. She also gives lots of practice problems, and I found her weekly assignments helpful if you actually do them.

Her lectures are very clear and she makes sure that everyone understands the concepts before moving on. Most of her lectures are based on the textbook, so missing a lecture is not such a big deal. She's also very helpful in and out of class!
